<note n="0753001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0753001">大願＋（海）【明】</note>
<note n="0753002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0753002">曰恐日. Maṇisūryacandravidyotitaprabhā.</note>
